com.sap.spe.condmgnt.customizing

Interface IAccess

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface IAccess
extends java.io.Serializable
    Interface for an access-object. This object is part of an access sequence. The access defines the key fields and the condition table for the search of condition records.
